Photo taken on Aug. 1, 2020 shows a view of the Band-e-Amir lakes after reopening to the public in Bamiyan province, Afghanistan. The scenic area has previously been closed for four months due to the COVID-19 epidemic. (Photo by Azimi/Xinhua) 

